        "content": "<p>I just created a <a href=\"https://github.com/WebAssembly/wasi-libc/issues/691\">new issue on wasi-libc</a> to discuss the design choices for a wasip3 port. </p>\n<p>Background: Basically I tried using cooperative thread built-ins with an enriched wasip2 and found that all of time, filesystem and sockets need to become p3 as well to make a cooperative <code>poll</code> possible ...</p>\n<div class=\"message_embed\"><a class=\"message_embed_image\" href=\"https://github.com/WebAssembly/wasi-libc/issues/691\" style=\"background-image: url(&quot;https://uploads.zulipusercontent.net/9ca1d8c4f20a2147434075a841ed7e889e10c746/68747470733a2f2f6f70656e67726170682e6769746875626173736574732e636f6d2f663339373162363961643232633866636237656463323330303331613761343963363665666531303739626364303163353534663063666366356337656463322f576562417373656d626c792f776173692d6c696263&quot;)\"></a><div class=\"data-container\"><div class=\"message_embed_title\"><a href=\"https://github.com/WebAssembly/wasi-libc/issues/691\" title=\"WebAssembly/wasi-libc\">WebAssembly/wasi-libc</a></div><div class=\"message_embed_description\">WASI libc implementation for WebAssembly. Contribute to WebAssembly/wasi-libc development by creating an account on GitHub.</div></div></div>",
